lyrics.stanza:
Softly and tenderly Jesus is calling&mdash;
  Calling for you and for me;
Patiently Jesus is waiting and watching&mdash;
  Watching for you and for me!

Why should we tarry when Jesus is pleading&mdash;
  Pleading for you and for me?
Why should we linger and heed not His mercies&mdash;
  Mercies for you and for me?

Time is now fleeting, the moments are passing&mdash;
  Passing from you and from me;
Shadows are gathering, death-beds are coming&mdash;
  Coming for you and for me!

Oh, for the wonderful love He has promised&mdash;
  Promised for you and for me!
Though we have sinned, He has mercy and pardon&mdash;
  Pardon for you and for me!
